title: Bitches, watch my video please

embed.description: I prank call Adelaide 5aa Talkback radio host Bob Francis and tell him that I know he has a small willy. Bob quickly becomes abusive as usual and calls me a dick brain. Bob Francis is Australia's longest on air talk back radio host

body: Hey my fellow LoL nerd pals. Last time I posted one of my prank calls the entire community gave me nothing but hate for calling the radio host fat.. What about this one? Is it any better?

replies.body:
> HEY I GOT A GOOD IDEA. LET'S JUST CALL SOMEONE AND BE EXTREMELY %%%%ING RUDE AND POST IT ON YOUTUBE. I BET I WILL GET 1MILLION VIEWS. IT'S SO FUNNY
